Jeff is pushing on a door with a horizontal force of [`F_J = [$fj]`] [`N`]. The moment arm of this force around the hinges of the door is [`d_1 = [$d1]`] [`cm`]. Ted is pushing in the opposite direction on the other side of the door. The moment arm of his pushing force is [`d_2 = [$d2]`] [`cm`]. How large is the force that Ted pushes with if the door is in static equilibrium?

